title: How to Do a Short Messy Hairstyle | AXE | Instagroom
description:
The only messy thing about Diogo is his hair. This is how he messes it up. 

THE TOOLS:
AXE Urban Messy Look Flexible Paste 

THE STEPS:
1. Blow-dry 
2. Mix one finger of paste
3. Squeeze that thing
4. Mess it up

transcripts: The only thing messy about me is my hair. When I wake up I wash my hair, I dry it a little bit, I take one finger of paste and I put it in my hair. When I see it’s really messy, it’s done.
